      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Ibn Fazzal, from Ali Bin Uqba, from Ayoub Bin Rashid, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Whatever from the Hadeeth is not in accordance with the Quran, so it is a décor’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          " 4. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from ibn Faddal from Ali ibn ‘Uqba from Ayyub ibn Rashid from abu ‘Abdallah (a.s.) who has said the following. “Of Hadith whatever does not agree with the holy Quran is a useless statement.”"
        ]
      }
